            <lg xml:id="TK1178">
<l>pēṇātu peṭṭā ruḷarmaṉṉō maṟṟavark </l>
<l> kāṇā tamaivila kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is indeed here who loved me with his lips but not with his heart but mine eyes suffer from not seeing him.</l>
